result.name: Showtime Sports Bar

reviews.text: Not really a sports bar, came to watch the epl but they wouldn’t put volume on just Cantonese dance music over the top. We were greated and treated very rudely by one of the wait staff, others where nice but one in particular was incredibly rude. They made in feel very uncomfortable and unwelcome. Food was average at best and food and drinks are over priced for what you get. Wouldn’t recommend as a “sports bar” or a place to eat more about the beer pong and pool it seems
variety of game are available in the bar. won't get bored with all these entertainment.
